Package: novavm
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Maintainer: Haris <harishsg99@gmail.com>
Description: Lightweight microVM hypervisor with eBPF observability
 NovaVM runs OCI container images inside real KVM virtual machines
 with eBPF observability, OPA policy enforcement, and 4-level caching
 for sub-100ms warm boot times.
 .
 Features:
  - KVM-based VM isolation (not just namespaces)
  - 69ms warm boot via L3 snapshot restore
  - Real-time eBPF observability (host + guest)
  - OPA admission control + runtime enforcement
  - OCI image support (Docker Hub, GHCR, Quay)
Homepage: https://github.com/novavm/novavm
